					  FINAL RESULTS: 2011 OPGA Ohio Public Links Golf Championship  

					 by Allen Freeman  |  July 29, 2011    No Comments  

					 

 Congratulations to Kevin Miller of Dover, who successfully defended his crown to repeat as champion in the 2011 Ohio Publinx! Final results from the 2011 Ohio Public Links Championship, a 72-hole individual stroke play event conducted by the Ohio Public Golfers Association at Seven Hills Golf Club in Hartville, Ohio, July 26th – July 29th:   [Read more ?]  

					 

					   

			

					
			

					  FINAL RESULTS: 2011 Ohio Publinx Mid-Am  

					 by Allen Freeman  |  May 15, 2011    No Comments  

					 

 Adam Arnett of Columbus outlasted Mark Hunnicutt of Howard to win the 2011 Ohio Public Golfers Association Mid-Amateur Championship. Played May 14th and 15th at the Chapel Hill Golf Course in Mt. Vernon, Ohio, this state 36-hole stroke play tournament requires players to be age of 25 or over to compete. Complete results follow:   [Read more ?]  

					 

					   

			

					
			

					  Seven Hills to Host Ohio Publinx Championship in 2011 and 2012  

					 by Allen Freeman  |  February 14, 2011    No Comments  

					 

 Stark County will once again play host to a state amateur ‘major’: the Ohio Public Golfers Association (OPGA) State Public Links Championship (better known as the Ohio Publinx) will be played at the  Seven Hills Golf Course  in Hartville, Ohio in 2011 and 2012.   [Read more ?]  

					 

					   

			

					
			

					  FINAL RESULTS: 2010 Ohio Senior Publinx  

					 by Allen Freeman  |  September 12, 2010    No Comments  

					 

 John Zitkovic of Findlay shot a sizzling score of 5-under par 139 in the 2010 Ohio Senior Public Links Championship this weekend at Hiawatha Golf Club in Mt. Vernon, earning a one shot victory over Rich Miller of Columbus. 
 2010 Cleveland Senior Am champ Norton Brick of Elyria finished in third place at 2-under par 142, while Lynn Martin of Findlay finished fourth another shot back.  
 And Lorain County legend Jerry Fisher of Amherst summoned some of his good feelings from Ohio Publinx events of yore to grab a solid T5 finish with an even par score of 144! Complete results follow…   [Read more ?]  

					 

					   

			

					
			

					  FINAL RESULTS: 2010 Ohio Publinx Championship  

					 by Allen Freeman  |  August 6, 2010    No Comments  

					 

 Kent State player Kevin Miller of Dover won the 2010 OPGA Publinx State Championship Tournament at Cooks Creek Golf Club in Ashville, Ohio today, finishing at 9-under par 279 and a three-shot victory over a trio of players.  [Read more ?]  

					 

					   

			

					
			

